import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' import axiosInstance from '../../baseurl' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' function CreateChat() { const [Doctors, setdocs] = useState([]) useEffect(()=>{ axiosInstance.post(`/viewAllDoctors`) .then((res)=>{console.log(res) setdocs(res.data.data)}) .catch((err)=>{console.log(err);}) },[]) return (
{Doctors.length?Doctors.map((a)=>{ return (
{a.name}

specialization : {a.specialization}

Contact : {a.contact}

Chat
) }):
No Doctors available
}
) } export default CreateChat
